<h2 id="100">1. What is plentyBI?</h2>
<div class="sectionbody">
<div class="paragraph">
<p>plentyBI is a business intelligence tool that is directly integrated in your plentymarkets system. You can use plentyBI to keep track of important key figures and data of your business at any time. The high number of available settings allows you to provide transparency and make clever business decisions whenever you want.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div><div class="sect1">
